# Playable Builder Kit

**Start:** `ai/README.md` → `ai/INSTRUCTIONS.md` → `ai/SKILLS-INDEX.md`

**Install / setup:** `playable-setup` rule → `bash scripts/setup-env.sh --yes` (after user approves).

**Create new playable:** `ai/skills/playable-create-workflow/SKILL.md` + `ai/CLI-MAP.md` → `pnpm playable:new`

| Task | Skill under `ai/skills/` |
|------|--------------------------|
| **Reply to Marketing (short)** | `playable-mkt-response` — after every create/edit/delete |
| **Create playable (ask first)** | `playable-create-workflow` |
| Single HTML deliverable | `playable-single-file-deliver` |
| New page | `playable-new-route` |
| Viewport shell (UI = mobile only) | `playable-viewport-shell` — mandatory |
| CSS 390×844 (font, margin, padding tỷ lệ màn) | `playable-mobile-scaling` — mandatory |
| Images / Lucide | `playable-assets` |
| Lottie | `playable-lottie` |
| Store CTA | `playable-store-cta` |
| Interactions | `playable-interactions` |
| AppLovin | `playable-applovin-compliance` |
| **Template/playable isolation** | `playable-data-isolation` — mandatory for template/playable JSON edits |

Build: `pnpm build:single <page>` then `pnpm verify:applovin <page>`.

`ai/skills/` = AI docs. `src/skills/` = JavaScript only.
